    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This example features the S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of engineering boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for optimized cam phasing. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been proactively maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and Powerflex bushings to mitigate floor pan fatigue. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh featuring a high-flow water pump. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the engine's compression remains within factory spec and the suspension geometry is dialed for precision. This is a high-performance machine ready for the twisties, sitting on staggered Style 67 alloys wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
